$ Oracle: automatic indexing

Enabling automatic indexing
code {
begin
   → development/databases/Oracle/installed/packages/dbms/auto_index[dbms_auto_index].configure('AUTO_INDEX_MODE', 'IMPLEMENT');
end;
/
code }

In 21c, the → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters[init parameter] `optimizer_session_type` can be set to `ADHOC` in a
→ development/databases/Oracle/architecture/session to suspend automatic indexing for queries that are executed from this session.

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/objects/indexes[Indexes]
